Text: MidYear PRC Cc like to update you on the progress we have made on Energy Ops midyear review process All of the Needs Improvement evaluations have been executed except for two which will be executed before the deadline We still need to review Satisfactory evaluations Our target date for this process is September st Please forward your Satisfactory evaluations to myself or Hector McLoughlin by September st so we can review them and move forward in the process Thank you for your help Anne Marie Allex

Final PRC Results Cc Attached is the final results from the meeting today These results DO NOT include the Analyst and Associates The spreadsheet contains an overall picture of the meeting today and a breakdown by organization EOPS EGM EIM There are also four charts which display the overall meeting and the breakdowns as well I have sent a copy to Bob Hall which DOES NOT include the VP rankings Please let me know if you need any other data Great meeting today Have a wonderful weekend Anne Marie

Analyst DistributionAttached is the distribution for All Analyst and the distribution for Analyst and You dont really get much data by breaking them down because the groups are so small but the overall combined graph provides some insight Let me know if you need anything else Anne Marie
